TRACEABLE WATERMARK

All source code contains the unique watermark: AEVA-2026-LQC-dc68e33

This watermark:
- Identifies the original source
- Tracks usage and derivatives
- Must remain in all copies and derivatives
- Removal is strictly prohibited

Watermark verification:
```bash
grep -r "AEVA-2026-LQC-dc68e33" aeva/ | wc -l
# Should return: 93 (number of source files)
```

DERIVATIVE WORKS

When creating derivative works:

1. Maintain original copyright notices
2. Keep the watermark (AEVA-2026-LQC-dc68e33)
3. Add your own copyright for your modifications
4. Clearly indicate changes made
5. Follow the same license restrictions

Example:
```
Original: AEVA by AEVA Development Team (AEVA-2026-LQC-dc68e33)
Modified by: [Your Name/Company]
Changes: [Description]
License: [Same restrictions apply]
```

